data.description: Orchard Park! Prepare to be impressed by this extremely well maintained FOUR bedroom, 1 1/2 bath home with a HUGE yard! You are greeted by an entry way leading down to a large living room full of natural light with glass block windows. Immediately as you enter the front door you enter the formal dining room with "Bow Windows" that adds more natural light. From there you will find an updated kitchen featuring granite countertops, soft close cabinets, built in spice rack, touch kitchen faucet and an abundance of cabinet space and stainless steel appliances that stay. The kitchen leads to a patio and an incredible backyard with apple trees and blackberry bushes. Enjoy your summer nights eating out on the patio! First floor 1/2 bath. Upstairs you will find four bedrooms with hardwood floors and a full bathroom. Newer (2015) furnace , and tear off roof. Upstairs vinyl windows 4 years old. This home  has been meticulously maintained inside and out! Nothing to do but move in!
